column2: Ranch Armor Polaris Ranger 1500 Mud Flaps/Fender Flares (Front & Back)
column3:
Polaris Ranger 1500 Fenders that push the fabrication boundary. A one-piece front fender, and two-piece rear keep the mud and debris off your Ranger. Design and attention to detail on our 1500 fenders is on a whole new level of precision.

Full aluminum construction that is both machine, and hand crafted. Our fabricators start with a sheet of aluminum, and laser cut it to perfection. Following the laser is our robotic press-break to form the fenders. Finally, our welders use the art of TIG welding to bring the material and shape together.

On the home stretch we prepare the 1500 fenders for coating by polishing some of the weld seems to a smooth finish. The fenders now have to undergo a strict acid wash and powder coat finish.

Polaris introduced the Polaris Ranger 1500 to the world as the most expensive production UTV, ever. At Ranch Armor, our goal is to keep your unit looking amazing with our new fenders.

Installation is simple and will only take even a novice person 20-30 minutes for all 4 fenders.

Ranch Armor products are 100% Born and Built in Texas. We will never outsource like some of our competition. Support American jobs!¬†¬†

column2: CFMoto UForce Quick Connect High Seat
column3:
A Quick Connect High Seat for your CFMoto UForce is here!¬†Ranch Armor is the leading manufacture of high seats for UTV's worldwide. Ranch Armor High Seats are crafted by a passionate team who cares about building the absolute best.¬†

Our Ranch Armor CFMoto UForce high seat features strategically located fixtures to lock seat to bed-side factory slots. This helps assure that the bed won't warp or bend outward from seat and weight over-time.¬†To secure the seat to the seat down to the bed we include 4x heavy-duty aluminum turn buckles that connect from seat to factory bed latches, as well as safety brackets that tie seat to rear of roll chassis. Install is a breeze and can be done in less than 10 minutes.¬†

Getting in and out of the high seat is simple and convenient with folding ladders on both sides. The ladders use tread plate (commonly known as diamond plate) steps to help with grip when its wet and your boots are caked with mud! Foot platform is laser cut with a double return press on both sides out of 14 gauge tread plate. Nut certs are welded into the center front of the foot platform to allow for easy installation of rifle mounts. Drains are laser cut on floor plate to allow water, mud, etc, to fall into bed and not sit on surface.¬†

CFMoto UForce Quick Connect High Seat Specifications:

  • Sail cloth UV, Marine, Mildew resistant fabric/canvas (10x stronger then vinyl)

  • Side Baskets (Cup Holders)

  • Folding ladders that are removable

column2: Polaris Ranger 1500 Quick Connect High Seat
column3:
The first available high seat for your Polaris Ranger 1500 is here!¬†Ranch Armor is the largest high seat manufacture in the world and we continuously look for ways to improve our design.¬†

Our Ranch Armor Ranger 1500 high seat features strategically located fixtures to lock seat to integrated Polaris bed rail. This helps assure that the bed won't warp or bend outward from seat and weight over-time.¬†To secure the seat to the seat down to the bed we include 4x heavy-duty aluminum turn buckles that connect from seat to factory bed latches, as well as safety brackets that tie seat to rear of roll chassis. Install is a breeze and can be done in less than 10 minutes.¬†

Getting in and out of the high seat is simple and convenient with folding ladders on both sides. The ladders use tread plate (commonly known as diamond plate) steps to help with grip when its wet and your boots are caked with mud! Foot platform is laser cut with a double return press on both sides out of 14 gauge tread plate. Nut certs are welded into the center front of the foot platform to allow for easy installation of rifle mounts. Drains are laser cut on floor plate to allow water, mud, etc, to fall into bed and not sit on surface.¬†

Polaris Ranger 1500 Quick Connect High Seat Specifications:

  • Constructed of steel¬†
  • Sail cloth UV, Marine, Mildew resistant fabric/canvas (10x stronger then vinyl)
  • Marine medium firm foam cushions
  • Laser-cut plate legs provide great look and exceptional support
  • Side Baskets (Cup Holders)
  • Adjustable/Removable rifle/grab bar
  • Folding ladders that are removable
  • Textured powder coat standard
  • Lifetime warranty on construction

column3:
Features¬†

  • Adjustable heat-treated collars for camber adjustability with a 1‚Äù thread
  • Ladder bar compatible with the 1.5‚Äù ID clamps
  • Extreme duty 1.5‚Äù x .120‚Äù DOM steel construction

Heavy Duty Strength
High Lifter‚Äôs new heavy duty control arms add more support than factory. Our upper and lower arms are made with the same material for added strength, so they can withstand the abuse applied during a typical ride. High Lifter arms are constructed out of 1.5‚Äù DOM with .120 wall tubing. This is a 40% increase in size and a 25% increase in steel thickness for added durability and strength.

Built in Adjustability
The lower arms also feature an adjustability component in the bushing collars to eliminate premature wearing that can come from the addition of lift kits, portals, or larger tires. When the kit is set to the factory position, you have 3/8‚Äù of adjustability camber in and out. Heat treated and plated adjustable bushing collars allow you to be confident in the strength you‚Äôre adding to your ride. This kit comes packaged and preadjusted to the factory position, and factory bushings and caps should be used for installation.

Increased Ground Clearance
We maximized ground clearance by strategically arching the lower control arm with double bends. This unique design allowed us to get an additional 1.75‚Äù of ground clearance to avoid impacting those nasty trail obstacles. These bends maintain the factory geometry, which helps reduce wear on components like axles.¬†

Tire Fitment: Up to 31"
Our tire fitment guide is a general fitment and is in no way guaranteed. Tires and lifts vary by manufacture and tire fitment can be affected by other modifications such as, but not limited to, wheel offset, actual tire diameter and actual tire width. High Lifter‚Äôs new heavy duty control arms add more support than factory. Our upper and lower arms are made with the same material for added strength, so they can withstand the abuse applied during a typical ride. High Lifter arms are constructed out of 1.5‚Äù DOM with .188 wall tubing. This is a 50% increase in size and a 70% increase in steel thickness for added durability and strength.

Built in Adjustability

When the kit is set to the factory position, you have 3/8‚Äù of adjustability camber in and out. We maximized ground clearance by strategically arching the lower control arm with double and TRIPLE bends. Portals and large tires apply torque that can distort the ball joint bracket, leading to failure of the arms. With over 130% increase in the ball joint mounting area, we are helping to prevent breakdown or ‚Äúegging‚Äù of the mounting bracket.

column3:

When you see this top in person, it is amazing the sheer size of it and how sharp/perfect it is considering just how long this aluminum sheet that makes up the body of top actually is.¬†

Ranch Armor is known for the toughest and most utilitarian UTV tops in the world. The Can-Am Defender Max Lonestar comes with a factory JL Audio top, and we realized most customers probably don't want to throw that top out the window. However, with the factory JL Top being plastic it doesn't stand a chance in terms of: Mounting Light Bars, Securing Cargo, or looking as badass as the machine itself is. With your new Max Rooftop Rack from Ranch Armor, your machine just became all that it can be.¬†

column2: Honda Pioneer 1000 Aluminum High Seat
column3:
The first and only Honda Pioneer 1000 Aluminum High Seat is here. Ranch Armor brings you a lightweight, ultra strong, and versatile high seat that bolts/secures to you Honda Pioneer 1000 bed. The large aluminum diamond plate foot platform provides plenty of room for standing. Ladders and rifle rest all tie into each other via a bent/notch design that utilizes 2" aluminum pipe. High seat legs are laser-cut 1/4" aluminum with reinforced upright supports.¬†¬†

If you would like additional storage you can add a rear upper high seat basket. Rear basket mounts to upper backrest and is TIG welded on. It is not removable once built with seat.¬†

Honda Pioneer 1000 high seats rest on the bed floor of your Pioneer and secure through factory bed mount holes.¬†

We use a local Texas based vendor for our cushions that are constructed using marine grade firm-foam, and Sail cloth. The Sail cloth is 10x more durable than vinyl and is fully water, weather, and mildew resistant. Don't worry, it has a poly-urethane coating on it that makes it glossy and smooth.¬†

All high seats come standard in a powder coat finish semi texture/semi-gloss.¬†

Honda Pioneer 1000 Aluminum High Seat Specifications:

  • Constructed of Aluminum
  • Sail cloth UV, Marine, Mildew resistant fabric/canvas (10x stronger then vinyl)
  • Marine medium firm foam cushions
  • Laser-cut plate legs provide great look and exceptional support
  • Standard textured powder coat¬†
  • Stationary ladders on both sides
  • Rifle rest/grab bar¬†
  • Lifetime warranty on construction

Ranch Armor High Seats are NOT to be ridden while vehicle is in motion. Please Note: Death or Serious Injury can occur.

column2: Can-Am Defender Overhead Audio/Speaker System
column3:
A fully contained ready-to-go Can-Am Defender overhead audio/speaker system that bumps. Clean and modern design will go nicely with either interior of your: Can-Am Defender Limited, or ANY open cab model Can-Am Defender. Here at Ranch Armor we did all the leg work to ensure you had a well-though-out system that could withstand the abuse and environments your UTV goes through.¬†The overhead speaker enclosure itself is laser cut and formed 1/8" aluminum, this means lightweight and no rust, ever! Of course, we had to make sure it was topped off with our durable powder coat finish.

On the audio side, we were sure to use one of the best in the business, Wet Sounds.¬†When partnering with Wetsounds on this, it was a no-brainer with their reputation in the marine audio/outdoor sound space. So yes, the system is marine grade... go ahead, get it wet or dirty. In between the speakers you have your Wetsounds headunit/controller and to the right will be your switch panel or cluster of switches. We have given you the option to use our switch panel (that comes with our Ranch Armor top light packages) OR use (if you choose) 3 spaces for standard rocker switches of your choosing. It doesn't matter which way you go, all the overhead audio systems arrive ready to for your application.

If you purchase a Ranch Armor top, this is an addition that can be added in place of a package 4 upgrade on the roof options side. If you already own a Ranch Armor top, no worries at all you can add this to it without any issues. If you don't own a Ranch Armor top, it will STILL arrive ready for you. In place of the switch panel (8 gang touch panel) you will have 3 open switch slots for standard rocker switches. So, let's say you have a plastic top with a couple of light bars you are installing, simply install your lights and run your wires to the overhead Ranch Armor speaker system, and utilize the 3 laser cut-out slots already built-in for your switches. We included a harness standard that will go down your roll bar and will utilize your Pulse Bar system. Of course, we hope you buy OR have a Ranch Armor top, but it is NOT required.

column2: CF Moto UFORCE 1000 XL Crew Metal Top
column3:
The new CF MOTO UForce 1000 Metal Top is here and brought to you by Ranch Armor UTV. We are the first company to bring viable options and accessories for the UForce 1000 Crew UTV and proud of it!¬†Like all of our UTV metal roofs, we first look at how we can add value to the vehicle in terms of: protection from the elements, space for cargo, and of course sturdiness. Style is second, but equally important with the overall goal of building the best metal tops possible for your CF MOTO UForce.

All RanchArmor tops are laser-cut and pressed to achieve the overall shape of the roof "shell". We then add reinforced sub-frame components under the top and in this case, 5 channels that run the length of the roof end-to-end to help us achieve a rigid and silent assembly. The UForce 1000 crew metal roof attaches via 6 points on the UForce's frame. 2 bolts in the front secure roof to factory slots in overhead roll-frame, while 4 stainless steel rubber coated loop-clamps secure to middle and rear roll frame.¬†

Due to the length of the UForce 1000 XL (Crew) model UTV,¬†ALL¬†roofs are what would normally be our optional "extended" versions right off the bat. The roof has a great overhand on the front that helps protect from the elements and is windshield friendly!¬†

CFMoto UForce 1000 XL Crew Metal Roof Specs

  • Steel Construction (Optional Aluminum Upgrade) with steel tubular/angle iron sub-frame
  • Textured Powder Coat standard¬†
  • 14 Gauge Steel Shell¬†(Optional 11 Gauge Aluminum Upgrade)
  • Rain ‚ÄúGutters‚Äù Front & Rear
  • Direct fitment using factory holes and loop clamp fasteners. Drilling of overhead front two holes is required for mounting. 2 bolts in front, 2 loop clamps in center, 2 loop clamps in rear.¬†
  • Lifetime Warranty on construction

CFMOTO UForce 1000 XL Metal Roof Compatibility:

  • 100% compatible with all: 2022+ UForce 1000 XL (Crew)¬†

column2: Quick Connect Mid-Size Polaris Ranger Aluminum High Seat
column3:
Polaris Ranger Mid-Size Quick Connect Aluminum Polaris Ranger high seat is here! Built specifically for the mid-size Polaris Ranger, our new aluminum mid-size high seat is packed with standard features. Our aluminum high seats are FULLY TIG welded, no spool guns here. Our department that handles aluminum production is of the absolute highest quality and attention to detail. Four aluminum pipe/tubes on the bottom-side of platform extend 2 inches into factory holes/slots on bed-sides creating a very snug and precise fit.¬†

A HUGE laser-cut and CNC press broke foot/standing platform runs the full width of bed making moving around and standing simple. The cushions themselves went through multiple phases of testing, We ruled out vinyl (tears and becomes weak in direct sunlight) and went with Sail Cloth automotive-grade convertible top canvas. The cushions are UV and water resistant fitted over a firm marine-grade foam.¬†Easily adjust removable rifle rack 6 inches up or down. Yes, high seat will fit through a standard garage door (our most common question) without any issues!¬†

  • Sail cloth UV, Marine, Mildew resistant fabric/canvas (10x stronger then vinyl)

  • Standard textured powder coat¬†

  • Rifle rest/Grab bar
  • Side baskets/cup holders standard

column2: Can-Am Defender Crew Max Limited Ultra Extended Aluminum Top
column3:
Ranch Armor brings the first aluminum one-piece UTV top that extends from the front of your Can-Am Defender Limited to the rear. The ultra light-weight aluminum top is supported by a sub-frame under the sheet metal aluminum shell in combination with the side racks. Holds plenty of weight and is very sturdy to stand on. Just like we were the first to bring a top that transitions all your Limited components over, we are the first to now bring that top available in the Ultra Extended length.

Our Ranch Armor Limited/HVAC tops including the ultra top seal better than factory, and transition all your factory headliner/overhead wiring harnesses over. This allows you to keep that factory interior look, and not have to relocate all the wiring and other overhead parts below the vehicle.¬†Our Ranch Armor Limited tops DO NOT void factory warranty as they DO NOT change or require any change to unit or electrical overhead, don't worry we got you covered! We include a weather seal that goes in between the roof sub-frame and the contact points of the roof/factory frame. The roof also includes rear window mounting bracket as you will see in the photos allowing you to connect rear glass windows in the way you do factory.

Can-Am Defender Crew Max Limited Ultra Extended Aluminum Top Specs:

  • Steel Construction with steel tubular/angle iron sub-frame (special place holders and channels for factory headliner transition)
  • Textured Powder Coat standard
  • 14 Gauge Steel Shell¬†(Optional 11 Gauge Aluminum Upgrade)
  • Rain ‚ÄúGutters‚Äù Front & Rear
  • Direct fitment using factory holes. Easily bolts on using 6 connections points. 2 Bolts into factory holes in the front, 2 clamps in the middle, and 2 clamps in the rear.¬†
  • Optional rear folding ladder for easy access to the top.¬†
  • Lifetime Warranty on construction

Can-Am Defender Crew Max Limited Aluminum Roof Compatibility:

  • 100% compatible with all: 2020+ Can-Am Defender Crew Max Limited Models.¬†
  • ***IMPORTANT*** If you have a 2022+/Newer Limited Lonestar, the factory overhead plastic audio top will NOT transition to our top. You would be getting rid of it.¬†

We include a weather seal that goes in between the roof sub-frame and the contact points of the roof/factory frame. The roof also includes rear window mounting bracket as you will see in the photos allowing you to connect rear glass windows in the way you do factory.

  • Rain ‚ÄúGutters‚Äù Front & Rear
  • Direct fitment using factory holes. Easily bolts on using 6 connections points. 2 Bolts into factory holes in the front, 2 clamps in the middle, and 2 clamps in the rear.¬†
  • Optional rear folding ladder for easy access to the top.¬†
  • Lifetime Warranty on construction

Can-Am Defender Crew Max Limited Metal Roof Compatibility:

column2: Mahindra Roxor Aluminum High Seat
column3:
Mahindra Roxor Aluminum High Seat by Ranch Armor is here! Direct bolt-in-design allows you to securely attach the high seat right to your factory Roxor. Our beautiful aluminum high seats use 1 1/2" round tube for primary construction. Large foot/standing platform gives passengers a great area to stand and walk on. Our standard rifle rest in the front of high seat is great for resting your gun on for longer distance shots.¬†

Important: MUST SELECT¬†Mahindra Roxor ROPS Model (has rear 45 degree roll bars going into rear bed corners) OR Mahindra Roxor NON ROPS (Rear bars have been removed OR will be removed to allow for larger high seat install).¬†

Side storage baskets are there to hold gear or your favorite beverage, standard.¬†¬†If you would like additional storage you can add a rear upper high seat basket which is optional. Rear upper baskets are constructed using aluminum sheet that are laser cut and formed. Edges on all baskets are returned at the top for a soft edge.¬†

Roxor Mahindra high seat sits on an angle iron platform or foundation that hugs the bed-rails on 2 sides. We have rear mounts that are pressed 3/16" brackets that bolt into rear factory holes. Front of seat uses heavy-duty tie-down/turn buckle anchors that secure front-end of seat to factory Mahindra bed-ties.¬†

The sail cloth canvas that is used on our cushions is 10x more durable than vinyl and is fully water, weather, and mildew resistant. Don't worry, it has a poly-urethane coating on it that makes it glossy and smooth.¬†

All high seats come standard with semi gloss/semi texture powder coat.¬†

MAHINDRA ROXOR ALUMINUM HIGH SEAT SPECIFICATIONS:

  • Aluminum Construction FULL TIG Construction
  • Sail cloth UV, Marine, Mildew resistant fabric/canvas (10x stronger then vinyl)
  • Marine medium firm foam cushions
  • Laser-cut plate legs provide great look and exceptional support
  • Standard powder coat
  • Bolt-on using factory Mahindra tie-down and bolt-down points¬†
  • Lifetime warranty on construction

Ranch Armor High Seats are NOT to be ridden while vehcle is in motion. Please Note: Death or Serious Injury can occur.¬†

column2: Polaris Ranger Overhead Audio/Speaker System
column3:
A fully contained ready-to-go Polaris overhead audio/speaker system that bumps. Clean and modern design will go nicely with either interior of your: Ranger Northstar, or ANY open cab model Polaris Full-Size Pro-Fit roll cage. Here at Ranch Armor we did all the leg work to ensure you had a well-though-out system that could withstand the abuse and environments your UTV goes through.¬†The overhead speaker enclosure itself is laser cut and formed 1/8" aluminum, this means lightweight and no rust, ever! Of course, we had to make sure it was topped off with our durable powder coat finish.

On the audio side, we were sure to use one of the best in the business, Wet Sounds.¬†When partnering with Wetsounds on this, it was a no-brainer with their reputation in the marine audio/outdoor sound industry. So yes, the system is marine grade... go ahead, get it wet or dirty. In between the speakers you have your Wetsounds headunit/controller and to the right will be your switch panel or cluster of switches. We have given you the option to use our switch panel (that comes with our Ranch Armor top light packages) OR use (if you choose) 3 spaces for standard rocker switches of your choosing. It doesn't matter which way you go, all the overhead audio systems arrive ready to for your application.

If you purchase a Ranch Armor top, this is an addition that can be added in place of a package 4 upgrade on the roof options side. If you already own a Ranch Armor top, no worries at all you can add this to it without any issues. If you don't own a Ranch Armor top, it will STILL arrive ready for you. In place of the switch panel (8 gang touch panel) you will have 3 open switch slots for standard rocker switches. So, let's say you have a plastic top with a couple of light bars you are installing, simply install your lights and run your wires to the overhead Ranch Armor speaker system, and utilize the 3 laser cut-out slots already built-in for your switches. We included a harness standard that will go down your roll bar and will utilize your Pulse Bar system. Of course, we hope you buy OR have a Ranch Armor top, but it is NOT required.

Need help with install? Simple Install Guide - Here

Upgrade your Polaris Ranger 1000 with the Ranch Armor Extended Aluminum Top, engineered for maximum durability, weather protection, and full-length coverage. This heavy-duty aluminum roof extends past the cab and over the bed, giving you more shade, better cargo protection, and a stronger overall platform‚Äîperfect for ranchers, hunters, landowners, and serious off-road users.

Built from high-strength aluminum, this top won‚Äôt crack, fade, or warp like plastic roofs. Its extended design shields your rear cargo area from the sun, rain, and debris while enhancing the look and utility of your Ranger. Precision-cut panels and reinforced mounting brackets ensure a perfect, rattle-free fit every time.

Boost the comfort, capability, and longevity of your Ranger 1000 with a roof system built to handle real work.

Key Features

  • Full-length coverage ‚Äì Extends over the cab and rear bed for superior protection.
  • Heavy-gauge aluminum construction ‚Äì Stronger and more durable than plastic or fiberglass tops.
  • Weather-resistant design ‚Äì Shields passengers and cargo from sun, rain, and debris.
  • Lightweight but extremely strong ‚Äì Won‚Äôt rust, warp, or crack.
  • Precision-fit mounting system ‚Äì Rattle-free installation designed specifically for the Polaris Ranger 1000.
  • Ranch Armor quality ‚Äì Built for ranch work, hunting, and demanding off-road conditions.

Specifications

  • Material: Heavy-gauge aluminum
  • Finish: Powder-coated¬†
  • Fitment: Polaris Ranger 1000 Full-Size Pro-Fit Open Cab Crew ONLY
  • Coverage: Extended length‚Äîcovers cab and full rear bed
  • Installation: Bolt-on, no cutting or fabrication required
  • Weight: Lightweight aluminum design (varies by configuration)

Perfect For

  • Ranching & farm work
  • Hunting setups
  • Off-road utility use
  • Sun & weather protection
  • Protecting cargo in the Ranger bed

¬†

column2: Can-Am Defender Max Limited HVAC Aluminum Top
column3:
Give your Can-Am Defender Limited the ultimate upgrade with the Ranch Armor Aluminum Top, engineered for maximum strength, all-weather protection, and a premium factory-fit appearance. Built from high-grade aluminum, this heavy-duty roof is designed to outperform plastic or fiberglass tops by offering superior durability, heat resistance, and long-term reliability‚Äîeven in the harshest ranch, hunting, and off-road environments.

Precision-cut and formed exclusively for the Defender Limited, the Ranch Armor aluminum top integrates seamlessly with your UTV‚Äôs cab and factory windshield system. Its rigid construction prevents rattling and flexing, while the lightweight aluminum design resists rust, dents, warping, and cracking. Whether you're battling intense sun, heavy rain, falling debris, or rugged terrain, this roof delivers year-round comfort and protection.

Built for people who rely on their machines, the Ranch Armor Can-Am Defender Limited Aluminum Top offers unmatched performance, a clean custom look, and the durability to last the life of your UTV.

Key Features

  • Premium aluminum construction ‚Äì Stronger, quieter, and more durable than plastic or composite roofs.
  • All-weather performance ‚Äì Shields the cab from sun, rain, snow, and falling debris.
  • Precision Defender Limited fitment ‚Äì Designed to integrate perfectly with factory cab and accessories.
  • Lightweight yet extremely strong ‚Äì No rusting, cracking, or fading over time.
  • Rattle-free design ‚Äì Reinforced mounting structure for a solid, stable fit.
  • Ranch Armor quality craftsmanship ‚Äì Built for ranch work, hunting, and tough off-road conditions. 100% Born and Built in Texas!

Specifications

  • Material: Heavy-gauge aluminum
  • Finish: Durable powder coat¬†
  • Fitment: Can-Am Defender Limited models
  • Installation: Bolt-on, no modification required
  • Weight: Lightweight aluminum approximately 90 pounds (depending on options)

Ideal For

  • Ranchers and property owners
  • Hunters and outfitters
  • Off-road and utility use
  • Extreme weather protection
  • Anyone replacing a weak or aging factory top

column2: Can-Am Defender Max Crew Aluminum Top
column3:
Can-Am Defender Max crew Aluminum Top that looks awesome and serves a utility purpose. All Ranch Armor tops are laser-cut and pressed to achieve the overall shape of the roof "shell". We then add reinforced sub-frame components under the top and in this case, 5 channels that run the length of the roof end-to-end to help us achieve a rigid and silent assembly. The Can-Am Defender crew aluminum roof attaches via 6 points on the Defender's frame. 2 bolts in the front secure roof to factory slots in overhead roll-frame, while 4 stainless steel rubber coated loop-clamps secure to middle and rear roll frame.¬†

Due to the length of the Can-Am Defender Max Crew model UTV,¬†ALL¬†tops are what would normally be our optional "extended" versions right off the bat. The roof has a great overhang on the front that helps protect from the elements and is windshield friendly!¬†

Can-Am Defender Max Aluminum Top Specs

  • Aluminum construction tubular/angle iron sub-frame
  • Textured Powder Coat standard
  • 11 Gauge Aluminum
  • Rain ‚ÄúGutters‚Äù Front & Rear
  • Direct fitment using factory holes and loop clamp fasteners. (Set the roof in place over the roll bar and use the pre-slotted holes on front of overhead pressed metal frame that came factory from Can-Am) No¬†modification, mounts perfectly to OEM Can-Am frame. 2 bolts in front, 2 loop clamps in center, 2 loop clamps in rear.¬†
  • Lifetime Warranty on construction

Can-Am Defender Max Aluminum Roof Compatibility:

  • 100% compatible with all: 2018+ Defender Max UTV's
  • Have full size doors? OR plan to put on full size doors? - Make sure you let us know you need "LOW PROFILE FLANGES" - in the Comment section at checkout or contact us directly to order.¬†

column2: Polaris Ranger Single NorthStar/HVAC Metal Top
column3:
Ranch Armor is the first to bring your a Polaris NorthStar HVAC Metal Top for your Ranger. Get rid of that factory Polaris top that leaks, before it blows off! Now you have an alternative that will bolt-on and seamlessly integrate factory headliner as well as overhead electrical harness that is in between. We mapped out and have built-in connection points as well as clip-slots for the factory harness to secure to just like it does stock. Get all the benefits of our Ranch Armor tops you don't get with the stock roof including: additional storage, standing platform, one-piece design, incredibly strong over factory plastic two-piece design, and of course a much better looking unit.¬†

Our Ranch Armor NorthStar tops DO NOT void factory warranty as they DO NOT change or require any change to unit or electrical overhead, don't worry we got you covered! Seals better then the factory roof that comes with the Ranger, it's true! We include a weather seal that goes in between the roof sub-frame and the contact points of the roof/factory frame. column2: Ranch Armor Polaris Ranger Block-Off/Vent Covers (Front & Rear)
column3:
Get rid of those open vent holes that Polaris has for their factory accessories/top. Ranch Armor has designed and engineered easy add-on block-off plates to seal and prevent airflow/water into your can. These work and are RECOMMENDED for all open cab model tops. They are INCLUDED with Polaris Ranger Northstar tops.

Includes 3 Sets for the front AND 1 large (50" wide) for the rear.¬†

Simply place in proper vent location using sandwich design plate (2 plates tighten together over an object), bolt together to tighten down, and you are done. We recommend using a silicone or RTV of some kind to 100% seal/create gasket around block-off plates. You can install these before or after your Ranch Armor roof install.¬†

POLARIS RANGER COMPATIBILITY:

  • 100% compatible with all: 2014+ model Polaris Ranger 570, 900, 1000 Full-Size Crew Pro-Fit Frames (Geometry overhead has not changed on Pro-Fit Frames)¬†

column2: Ranch Armor Polaris Ranger 1000 Northstar Ultra Extended Top
column3:
Ranch Armor brings the first one-piece UTV top that extends from the front of your Polaris Northstar all the way to the back of the bed. The roof is supported by a sub-frame under the sheet metal shell in combination with the side racks. Holds plenty of weight and is very sturdy to stand on. Just like we were the first to bring a top that transitions all your Northstar components over, we are the first to now bring that top available in the Ultra Extended length.

Our Ranch Armor Northstar/HVAC tops including the ultra top seal better than factory, and transition all your factory headliner/overhead wiring harnesses over. This allows you to keep that factory interior look, and not have to relocate all the wiring and other overhead parts below the vehicle.¬†Our Ranch Armor NorthStar tops DO NOT void factory warranty as they DO NOT change or require any change to unit or electrical overhead, don't worry we got you covered! We include a weather seal that goes in between the roof sub-frame and the contact points of the roof/factory frame. The roof also includes front/rear block-off plates and vent covers to seal up factory frame slots that would otherwise allow air/moisture in to cab.¬†

column2: Can-Am Defender Limited HVAC Single Cab Metal Top
column3:
The first Can-Am Defender Limited Single Cab HVAC Metal Top is here by Ranch Armor! We have developed a top that allows you to get rid of your low-quality/poorly engineered factory plastic top. No more leaking! No more blowing off while trailering, we got you covered!¬†

Now you have an alternative that will bolt-on and seamlessly integrate factory headliner as well as overhead electrical harness that is in between. We mapped out and have built-in connection points as well as clip-slots for the factory harness to secure to just like it does stock. Get all the benefits of our Ranch Armor tops you don't get with the stock roof including: additional storage, standing platform, one-piece design, incredibly strong over factory plastic design, and of course a much better looking unit.¬†

Our Ranch Armor Can-Am Limited tops DO NOT void factory warranty as they DO NOT change or require any change to unit or electrical overhead, don't worry we got you covered! Seals better then the factory roof that comes with the Defender, it's true! We include a weather seal that goes in between the roof sub-frame and the contact points of the roof/factory frame. The Ranch Armor Can-Am Limited Roof also includes a laser cut/CNC pressed rear mounting/block-off plate that connects/seals to roof and allows factory glass to seal against roof perfectly.¬†

CAN-AM DEFENDER SINGLE CAB LIMITED/HVAC MAX METAL TOP SPECS

  • Steel Construction (Optional Aluminum Upgrade) with steel tubular/angle iron sub-frame (special place holders and channels for headliner transition)
  • Textured Powder Coat standard (Optional Bed Liner Upgrade)
  • 14 Gauge Steel Shell¬†(Optional 11 Gauge Aluminum Upgrade)
  • Rain ‚ÄúGutters‚Äù Front & Rear
  • Direct fitment using factory holes. Easily bolts on using 4 bolts.¬†
  • Lifetime Warranty on construction

CAN-AM DEFENDER SINGLE CAB LIMITED/HVAC MAX METAL ROOF COMPATIBILITY:

  • 100% compatible with all: 2019+ Limited model Can-Am Defender Single Cab UTV's, including Pro (Long Bed) Limited Defenders

column2: Kawasaki Mule Pro MX Front Replacement Bumper
column3:
Just because you have the smaller Mule, doesn't mean it can't have a BIG attitude. The Ranch Armor Mule Pro MX Front Replacement Bumper gives your machine all the strength in the world to tackle anything! Hidden winch cubby mounts your winch behind front skid plate keeping winch tug/pull leverage lower where it needs to be. Easy install in less than 15 minutes!¬†

Construction is comprised of: steel 3/16" main vertical front beams, 2" Pipe, and 11 Gauge tread plate. All plate is laser cut and CNC press broke. Complete welded construction, done with beautiful attention to detail right here in Texas! The final step is an industrial ultra-durable powder coat (standard) finished to perfection.¬†¬†

Ranch Armor Bumpers are 100% Born and Built in Texas. We will NEVER outsource like some of our competition. Support American Jobs!¬†

Kawasaki Mule Pro MX Replacement Front Bumper Specs:

  • Steel Construction - combination of tread plate, flat plate, and pipe.¬†
  • 3/16" Vertical Laser Cut Crash/Bump Frame
  • 2‚Äù heavy duty pipe base
  • 1 1/2" heavy duty pipe headlight guards
  • Laser Cut and CNC Press Broke for a perfect fit
  • 11 GA Steel Plate Main Body
  • 2" Receiver Hitch
  • Textured Powder Coat Standard
  • Direct fitment using factory Kawasaki holes
  • Requires no vehicle modifications
  • Lifetime warranty on construction
  • Fits ALL Mule Pro MX Models

column2: Honda Pioneer Ranch Armor Front Replacement Bumper
column3:
Ranch Armor Honda Pioneer Front Replacement Bumper has been engineered from the inside out. Hidden winch cubby mounts your winch behind front skid plate keeping winch tug/pull leverage lower where it needs to be. Must have an aftermarket KFI or Warn winch bolt-on mount to securely fasten most winch's inside front factory winch cubby.¬†Bolts-on simply using factory Honda hardware.¬†

This is a FULL Front Replacement bumper, not a bull bar style half-guard. Our skid plate and protection covers the hood, headlights, front end all the way down to the differential/front drive-train with our skid plate.¬†

Construction is comprised of: steel 3/16" main vertical front beams, 2" Pipe, 1 1/2" heavy duty pipe headlight guards¬†and 11 Gauge tread plate. All plate is laser cut and CNC press broke. Complete welded construction, done with beautiful attention to detail right here in Texas! The final step is an industrial ultra-durable powder coat finished to perfection.¬†

Ranch Armor Bumpers are 100% Born and Built in Texas. We will never outsource like some of our competition. Support American jobs!¬†

Honda Pioneer Replacement Front Bumper Specs:

  • Steel Construction - combination of tread plate, flat plate, and pipe.¬†
  • Laser Cut and CNC Press Broke for a perfect fit
  • 2" heavy duty pipe main body
  • 1 1/2" heavy duty pipe headlight guards
  • Textured Powder Coat Standard
  • 11 GA Steel Plate Main Body
  • Direct fitment using factory Honda mounts.
  • 2" Receiver Hitch
  • Lifetime warranty on construction
  • Fits Honda Pioneer 1000 and 1000-5 (crew model)

NOTE: Winch Mounting Requires KFI #101965 Winch Mount

column2: Can-Am Defender Max Limited HVAC Metal Top
column3:
The first and only Can-Am Defender Limited/HVAC Metal Top is here by Ranch Armor. Get rid of that factory Can-Am top that is plastic and unreliable. Now you have an alternative that will bolt-on and seamlessly integrate factory headliner as well as overhead electrical harness that is in between. We mapped out and have built-in connection points as well as clip-slots for the factory harness to secure to just like it does stock. Get all the benefits of our Ranch Armor tops you don't get with the stock roof including: additional storage, standing platform, one-piece design, incredibly strong over factory plastic design, and of course a much better looking unit.¬†

Our Ranch Armor Can-Am Limited tops DO NOT void factory warranty as they DO NOT change or require any change to unit or electrical overhead, don't worry we got you covered! Seals better then the factory roof that comes with the Defender, it's true! We include a weather seal that goes in between the roof sub-frame and the contact points of the roof/factory frame. The Ranch Armor Can-Am Limited Roof also includes a laser cut/CNC pressed rear mounting/block-off plate that connects/seals to roof and allows factory glass to seal against roof perfectly.

CAN-AM DEFENDER LIMITED/HVAC MAX METAL TOP SPECS

  • Steel Construction (Optional Aluminum Upgrade) with steel tubular/angle iron sub-frame (special place holders and channels for headliner transition)
  • Textured Powder Coat standard
  • 14 Gauge Steel Shell¬†(Optional 11 Gauge Aluminum Upgrade)
  • Rain ‚ÄúGutters‚Äù Front & Rear
  • Direct fitment using factory holes. Easily bolts on using 4 bolts with no modification.¬†
  • Lifetime Warranty on construction

CAN-AM DEFENDER LIMITED/HVAC MAX METAL ROOF COMPATIBILITY:

  • 100% compatible with all: 2019+ Limited model Can-Am Defender Max UTV's

column2: Kawasaki Mule Pro FX/FXT Aluminum High Seat
column3:
Ranch Armor High Seats are NOT to be ridden while vehicle is in motion. Please Note: Death or Serious Injury can occur.¬†

A spacious and secure Aluminum Kawasaki Mule Pro FX/FXT High Seat is here! The bed is smaller, which left us with a challenge in creating a high seat that would allow for two large adults to sit up safely. The solution was quickly found which involved extending the butt portion of the seat out, and hang over the tailgate. Of course, we had to make sure the seat was safe. We tested it through the most extreme conditions including: massive incline and declines as well as roll-over/tip testing. Torture testing on the unit was done with riders equating to over 500 pounds up on the seat. Disclaimer: As always, we DO NOT recommend and are always against riding high seats while vehicle(s) are in motion.¬†

We INCLUDE 2 Under-Bed-Mount Braces that utilize factory bed-frame tubing to reinforce front bolt-down points of high seat.¬†

  • Sail cloth UV, Marine, Mildew resistant fabric/canvas (10x stronger then vinyl)
  • Marine medium firm foam cushions
  • Laser-cut plate legs provide great look and exceptional support
  • Choice of a textured powder coat (standard)¬†
  • Lifetime warranty on construction

column2: Can-Am Defender Feeder Storage Bumper
column3:
The Ranch Armor Can-Am Defender Feeder Bumper is the ultimate utility addition to your UTV. Easily bolt up the most impressive all-in-one front bumper on the market. Large platform up top for: storing gear, animals, corn for the built-in feeder, etc... One of the unique points of our bumper is the pull-through winch design that keeps your factory winch in original location. A channel that bolts in-place inside the feeder hopper goes over the winch cable keeping it out of the way and safe. Feeder holds approximately 50 pounds of corn. Installs in minutes!¬†

One of the most common complaints and down-sides we hear about bumper/feeder combos was: the feeder wobbles, it's in the way, it's ugly, it broke the welds on my hitch receiver of bumper (Not ours, of course). After much trial-and-error we came up with a clean design, and large storage capacity both above (gear) and below (corn/feed). A good bumper and feeder setup will cost around one thousand dollars when buying individually, our goal was to be around that price point, BUT with the bonus of getting a large storage rack up above to haul more gear! Not to mention, you don't have to take feeder on or off, and worry about it blocking your view sticking out a mile.¬†

Ranch Armor Bumpers are 100% Born and Built in Texas. We will never outsource like some of our competition. Support American jobs!¬†

Can-Am Defender Feeder & Cargo Bumper Specs:

  • Steel Construction
  • Textured Powder Coat Standard
  • 11 GA Steel Plate Main Body
  • Pressed/bent plate frame for rigidness
  • Direct fitment using factory holes. Use 4 factory holes on Can-Am Defender front-end to mount bumper.¬†

column3:
Mahindra Roxor High Seat by Ranch Armor is here! Direct bolt-in-design allows you to securely attach the high seat right to your factory Roxor. Our steel high seats primary construction is 1" square tube. Large foot/standing platform gives occupant a great area to stand and walk on. Our standard rifle rest in the front of high seat is great for resting your gun on for longer distance shots.¬†

Important: MUST SELECT Mahindra Roxor ROPS Model (has rear 45 degree roll bars going into rear bed corners) OR Mahindra Roxor NON ROPS (Rear bars have been removed OR will be removed to allow for larger high seat install).¬†

Side storage baskets are there to hold gear or your favorite beverage.¬†¬†If you would like additional storage you can add a rear upper high seat basket.

Roxor Mahindra high seat sits on an angle iron platform or foundation that hugs the bed-rails on 2 sides. We have rear mounts that are pressed 3/16" brackets that bolt into rear factory holes. Front of seat uses heavy-duty tie-down/turn buckle anchors that secure front-end of seat to factory Mahindra bed-ties.¬†

We use a local Texas based vendor for our cushions that are constructed using marine grade firm-foam, and Sail cloth. The Sail cloth is 10x more durable than vinyl and is fully water, weather, and mildew resistant. Don't worry, it has a poly-urethane coating on it that makes it glossy and smooth.¬†

All high seats come standard with semi gloss/semi texture powder coat. You can upgrade to bed liner for additional cost.¬†

MAHINDRA ROXOR HIGH SEAT SPECIFICATIONS:

  • Constructed of steel
  • Sail cloth UV, Marine, Mildew resistant fabric/canvas (10x stronger then vinyl)
  • Marine medium firm foam cushions
  • Laser-cut plate legs provide great look and exceptional support
  • Standard powder coat finish
  • Bolt-on using factory Mahindra tie-down and bolt-down points¬†
  • Lifetime warranty on construction

Ranch Armor High Seats are NOT to be ridden while vehicle is in motion. Please Note: Death or Serious Injury can occur.¬†

column2: Mahindra Roxor Metal Top
column3:
Ranch Armor is proud to offer the Mahindra Roxor Metal Roof. A robust utility top that is as tough as the Roxor itself. Direct bolt-on fitment utilizing 6 contact points that secure roof to the frame. Constructed using the latest laser-cutting and CNC press-break technology. All Ranch Armor metal tops incorporate sub-frame (tube and angle iron) construction that is welded to the sheet metal shell itself. Our tubular frame construction provides rigid platform should you stand or store materials on top.

As always, Texas Outdoors and Ranch Armor stand behind 100% American/Texas Made products. We NEVER outsource manufacturing and NEVER will. Build your Roxor metal top however you would like, see our options listed. If you don't see an option and want to go a custom route please contact us.¬†

Pictures shown vary with different roof setups/options customers have decided to do. Build your roof pretty much however you want with whatever you want, if you don't see a specific option listed, it doesn't mean we can't do it.¬†

MAHINDRA ROXOR METAL ROOF TOP SPECS

  • Steel Construction with steel tubular/angle iron sub-frame
  • Textured Powder Coat standard
  • 14 Gauge Steel Shell¬†
  • Upper Square Tube Rails (standard) utilizing 1" x 1" steel tube for a rugged and sturdy anchor point.¬†
  • Rain ‚ÄúGutters‚Äù Front & Rear
  • Direct bolt-on for easy installation. (Set the roof in place over the roll bar and use 6 provided steel/vinyl coated loop clamps to secure to roll frame) No¬†modification, mounts perfectly to OEM Polaris frame
  • Lifetime Warranty on construction

MAHINDRA ROXOR METAL ROOF TOP COMPATIBILITY:

  • 100% compatible with all: 2018+ (new models as well) model Mahindra Roxor

column2: Polaris Ranger 1000 Rear Bumper
column3:
Ranch Armor has brought you a rear replacement bumper for the Polaris Ranger (2018+) that makes your unit stronger, as well as looks great. Ranch Armor sets itself apart from the competition with our new bumper line for the Rangers. Our bumper mounts easily and securely to factory frame holes on bed chassis. Main construction is the 2" bent pipe combined with laser-cut and pressed tread plate.¬†

Hitch and LED Flush Mounts give your rear bumper even more capability. Full laser cut and CNC press broke components. All fabricated and made right here in Texas. Our welders and fabricators pay very close attention to every detail making sure you get a quality product that will last a lifetime.¬†

Ranch Armor Bumpers are 100% Born and Built in Texas. We will never outsource like some of our competition. Support American jobs!¬†

Polaris Ranger Replacement Rear Bumper Specs:

  • Steel Construction - combination of tread plate, flat plate, and pipe.¬†
  • Laser Cut and CNC Press Broke for a perfect fit
  • Textured Powder Coat Standard
  • 11 GA Steel Plate Main Body
  • Direct fitment using factory Polaris Mounts/Holes. Uses 4 factory bolt holes.
  • 2" Receiver Hitch
  • Lifetime warranty on construction
  • Fits Ranger and Ranger Crew

Legacy Rear Bumpers all Come STANDARD with: LED Flush Mounts, Rear Receiver Hitch, and Wiring Harness for LED Flush Mount Lights.¬†

REQUIRED - If you want to use your Ranch Armor bumper to tow, you must get our optional Hitch Support here.¬†

Designed specifically for the Polaris Ranger 1000 (all models, including XP and Crew), this rear bumper is crafted from heavy-duty American steel and engineered to withstand the toughest conditions on the job or off-road.

Whether you're hauling, towing, or navigating tight backcountry trails, Ranch Armor has your back‚Äîliterally. This bumper adds a solid layer of defense against impacts, brush, and debris while maintaining full utility bed function.

Key Features:

Model-Specific Fit: Engineered for 2020+ Polaris Ranger 1000, including XP and Crew models

Built to Last: Constructed from high-strength steel with a durable black powder-coated finish

Ranch-Proven Design: Protects rear-end components, tailgate, and lights from impact and trail damage

Easy Installation: Fully bolt-on with factory mounting points ‚Äì no drilling required

Made in the USA: Proudly designed and manufactured in Texas

Why Ranch Armor?
Ranch Armor is trusted by ranchers, hunters, and outdoor professionals for one reason: strength. When you depend on your UTV every day, you need accessories that can take a beating and keep performing. This rear bumper does just that‚Äîwith clean welds, smart design, and reliable protection that looks as good as it works.

**Add muscle to your Ranger 1000‚Äî**get the Ranch Armor Rear Bumper today and ride with confidence wherever the trail or job takes you.

column2: Can-Am Defender Single Cab Metal Top
column3:
Can-Am Defender single cab metal roof that looks awesome and serves a utility purpose. Like all of our UTV metal roofs, we first look at how we can add value to the vehicle in terms of: protection from the elements, space for cargo, and of course sturdiness. Style is second, but equally important with the overall goal of building the best metal tops possible for your Can-Am Defender.¬†

All RanchArmor tops are laser-cut and pressed to achieve the overall shape of the roof "shell". We then add reinforced sub-frame components under the top and in this case, 5 channels that run the length of the roof end-to-end to help us achieve a rigid and silent assembly. The Can-Am Defender single cab metal roof attaches via 4 points on the Defender's frame. 2 bolts in the front secure roof to factory slots in overhead roll-frame, while 2 stainless steel rubber coated loop-clamps secure to middle and rear roll frame.¬†

Due to the length of the Can-Am Defender Single Cab model UTV,¬†ALL single cab¬†roofs are what would normally be our optional "extended" versions right off the bat. The roof has a great overhand on the front that helps protect from the elements and is windshield friendly!¬†

Can-Am Defender Single Cab Metal Roof Specs

  • Steel Construction with steel tubular/angle iron sub-frame
  • Textured Powder Coat standard
  • 14 Gauge Steel Shell¬†(Optional 11 Gauge Aluminum Upgrade)
  • Rain ‚ÄúGutters‚Äù Front & Rear
  • Direct fitment using factory holes and loop clamp fasteners. (Set the roof in place over the roll bar and use the pre-slotted holes on front of overhead pressed metal frame that came factory from Can-Am) No¬†modification, mounts perfectly to OEM Can-Am frame. 2 bolts in front, 2 loop clamps in rear.¬†
  • Lifetime Warranty on construction
  • Have full size doors? OR plan to put on full size doors? - Make sure you let us know you need "LOW PROFILE FLANGES" - in the Comment section at checkout or contact us directly to order.¬†

column2: Polaris Ranger Aluminum High Seat
column3:
The ultimate Polaris Ranger Aluminum High Seat is here. Ranch Armor brings you a lightweight, ultra strong, and versatile high seat that easily connects to your Polaris Ranger bed. The large aluminum diamond plate foot platform provides plenty of room for standing. Ladders and rifle rest all tie into each other via a bent/notch design that utilizes 1 1/2" aluminum pipe. High seat legs are laser-cut 1/4" aluminum with reinforced upright supports.¬†¬†

If you would like additional storage you can add a rear upper high seat basket for additional cost. Rear basket mounts to upper backrest and is TIG welded on. It is not removable once built with seat.¬†

Ranch Armor aluminum Polaris Ranger high seat sits on an 3/16" aluminum angle iron platform or foundation that hugs the bed-rails around the diameter of the bed (front, left, and right). Welded 3/16"" thick tie-down anchors on the bottom of the high seat foundation are what's used to latch and tighten seat frame to CanAm factory bed tie-downs.

We use a local Texas based vendor for our cushions that are constructed using marine grade firm-foam, and Sail cloth. The Sail cloth is 10x more durable than vinyl and is fully water, weather, and mildew resistant. Don't worry, it has a poly-urethane coating on it that makes it glossy and smooth.¬†

All high seats come standard mild gloss/mild texture powder coat.¬†

Ranch Armor High Seats are NOT to be ridden while vehicle is in motion. Please Note: Death or Serious Injury can occur.

column2: Can-Am Defender Aluminum High Seat
column3:
The ultimate Can-Am Defender Aluminum High Seat is here. Ranch Armor brings you a lightweight, ultra strong, and versatile high seat that easily connects to your Can-Am Defender bed. The large aluminum diamond plate foot platform provides plenty of room for standing. Ladders and rifle rest all tie into each other via a bent/notch design that utilizes 2" aluminum pipe. High seat legs are laser-cut 1/4" aluminum with reinforced upright supports.¬†¬†

If you would like additional storage you can add a rear upper high seat basket. Rear basket mounts to upper backrest and is TIG welded on. It is not removable once built with seat.¬†

CanAm Defender high seat sits on an 3/16" aluminum angle iron platform or foundation that hugs the bed-rails around the diameter of the bed (front, left, and right). Welded 3/16" thick tie-down anchors on the bottom of the high seat foundation are what's used to latch and tighten seat frame to CanAm factory bed tie-downs.

We use a local Texas based vendor for our cushions that are constructed using marine grade firm-foam, and Sail cloth. The Sail cloth is 10x more durable than vinyl and is fully water, weather, and mildew resistant. Don't worry, it has a poly-urethane coating on it that makes it glossy and smooth.¬†

All high seats come in a powder coat finish semi texture/semi-gloss.¬†¬†

Can-Am Defender Aluminum Quick Connect High Seat Specifications:

  • Constructed of Aluminum
  • Sail cloth UV, Marine, Mildew resistant fabric/canvas (10x stronger then vinyl)
  • Marine medium firm foam cushions
  • Laser-cut plate legs provide great look and exceptional support
  • Standard textured powder coat
  • Stationary ladders on both sides
  • Rifle rest/grab bar¬†
  • Lifetime warranty on construction

Ranch Armor High Seats are NOT to be ridden while vehicle is in motion. Please Note: Death or Serious Injury can occur.

column2: Can-Am Defender Ranch Armor Front Roll Bar Basket Rack
column3:
The Ranch Armor Can-Am Defender front roll bar basket we offer spans 55 inches wide. Our front basket rack easily mounts direct to the side factory roll frame slots. Like all of our storage items we try and always stay away from U-bolts, especially when attaching baskets to frames. In the case of the Can-Am Defender storage basket, it bolts on with the included low-profile mounts.

Basket frame construction is 1" pipe wrapped with an expanded metal mesh. The expanded metal allows you to put small and compact gear/loose items without worrying about them falling out. The standard coating is a moderate textured powder coat, also available in a bed-liner.

Installation is very simple and takes about 10 minutes. Weight capacity of basket is more than you will ever need, believe us we have toted humans (big ones) around sitting in baskets. Of course, we do NOT condone the transport of people in the front roll bar basket.

column2: Fortress Tip-Out Windshield Polaris (1000)
column3:
Fortress tip out windshield for the Polaris 1000 models is a solid option. Simply put, it allows for a mode that keeps windshield all the way open, or a vent mode (approximately 5 inches outward) allowing just air circulation.¬†

A powder coated metal frame that is formed perfectly to the front and overhead roll bar frame securely snugs the Fortress windshield with loop clamps. No noise, no rattle, no squeaks! Works with most roofs on the market including our Ranch Armor metal tops. 2 gas shocks hold the windshield up when in upright position. Handle used to lock window down also acts as the prop lock to hold window in "vent" mode.¬†

This windshield works with new body style 1000 units ONLY. 2018+ model year.¬†

column2: Ranch Armor Polaris Ranger Feeder Bumper Front Rack
column3:
The new Ranch Armor Polaris Ranger Feeder Bumper is here. Store up to 100 pounds of corn with storage on top for: gear, supplies, or animals. Bolts directly to the factory Polaris frame (2018+ new body style) within minutes. Spinner is an inverted design so it hangs down very low. Even if you are worried about hitting rocks, branches, or debris don't worry we have engineered a very robust guard to protect the spinner and vehicle.¬†

One of the most common complaints and down-sides we hear about bumper/feeder combos was: the feeder wobbles, it's in the way, it's ugly, it broke the welds on my hitch receiver of bumper. After much trial-and-error we came up with a clean design, and large storage capacity both above (gear) and below (corn/feed). A good bumper and feeder setup will cost around one thousand dollars when buying individually, our goal was to be around that price point, BUT with the bonus of getting a large storage rack up above to haul more gear! Not to mention, you don't have to take feeder on or off, and worry about it blocking your view sticking out a mile.¬†

Tread plate platform allows hundreds of pounds of cargo, and the integrated winch platform allows for most winches to bolt right on.¬†

Ranch Armor Bumpers are 100% Born and Built in Texas. We will never outsource like some of our competition. Support American jobs!¬†

Polaris Ranger Feeder & Cargo Bumper Specs:

  • Steel Construction
  • Textured Powder Coat Standard
  • 11 GA Steel Plate Main Body
  • Pressed/bent plate frame for rigidness
  • Direct fitment using factory holes. Use 4 factory holes on Polaris front-end to mount bumper.¬†
  • Inverted Spinner Head with wired remote control included

****REQUIRES LIFT AND/OR LARGER TIRE SETUP****

column3:

Get just the roof with standard upper racks, or deck it out with optional LED Light Bars/Work Lights, Protective Face-Mask/Cages, or add a marine Bluetooth audio system to jam out!

The roof mounts solid and becomes "one with the vehicle" so no noise, and don't worry it's not coming off when hauling down the highway!

column2: EZ GO Golf Cart Aluminum Front Cargo & Storage Basket
column3:
All aluminum front EZ-GO Golf Cart cargo and storage basket is a must for any beach OR community that allows golf carts. Easily haul any kind of: small/medium/large-sized coolers, groceries, beach gear, tools, etc... You will quickly find so many uses for your new front basket. Holds up to 75 pounds with ease, so you can get everything you need in one trip.¬†

The aluminum tubing and expanded metal construction that makes up our EZ-GO basket weighs only 10 pounds. Two laser-cut and pressed aluminum plate brackets with pre-slotted holes for the included stainless steel clamps allow basket to bolt right-on with ease. No drilling or modification needed, and is ready-to-go in less than 10 minutes.¬†

column2: Kawasaki Mule Pro FX/FXT Feeder & Cargo Bumper
column3:
New Ranch Armor Kawasaki Mule Pro Feeder & Cargo Bumper is a sleek all-in-one must have! Get the best of 3 wolds with one UTV Bumper. 100 pounds of corn, huge upper flat surface for 500+ pounds of cargo and storage, coupled with a meaty bumper to plow through anything!¬†

We sell a lot of UTV bumpers, and we do a lot of UTV outfits that include a bumper AND a feeder. One of the most common complaints and down-sides we hear about was: the feeder wobbles, it's in the way, it's ugly, it broke the welds on my hitch receiver of bumper. After much trial-and-error we came up with a clean design, and large storage capacity both above (gear) and below (corn/feed). A good bumper and feeder setup will cost you almost a grand, our goal was to be around that price point, BUT with the bonus of getting a large storage rack up above to haul more gear! Not to mention, you don't have to take feeder on or off, and worry about it blocking your view sticking out a mile.¬†

All of the tread plate (aka diamond plate) is 11 GA or 1/8" thick steel. Construction consists of laser cut/pressed body, welded together. Feeder/trap door has oil-sealed stainless steel hinges. We always use an industrial grade 50/50 powder coat that has a mild texture/mild gloss finish. Worried about feeder components? Don't worry at all, we use only All Seasons Feeder components such as the spinner for quality long-life usage.¬†

Don't worry about fitment, it bolts right on in-place of factory bumper with factory hardware.¬†

Ranch Armor Bumpers are 100% Born and Built in Texas. We will never outsource like some of our competition. Support American jobs!¬†

Kawasaki Mule Pro Feeder & Cargo Bumper Specs:

  • Steel Construction
  • Textured Powder Coat Standard
  • 11 GA Steel Plate Main Body
  • Pressed/bent plate frame for rigidness
  • Direct fitment using factory holes. Uses 5 factory bolts from factory Mule Pro FX/FXT Bumper
  • All-Seasons Spinner Head with wired remote control included
  • Lifetime warranty on construction

****REQUIRES LIFT AND/OR LARGER TIRE SETUP****

column2: Can-Am Defender Max Crew Metal Top
column3:
Can-Am Defender Max crew metal roof that looks awesome and serves a utility purpose. Like all of our UTV metal roofs, we first look at how we can add value to the vehicle in terms of: protection from the elements, space for cargo, and of course sturdiness. Style is second, but equally important with the overall goal of building the best metal tops possible for your Can-Am Defender.¬†

All RanchArmor tops are laser-cut and pressed to achieve the overall shape of the roof "shell". We then add reinforced sub-frame components under the top and in this case, 5 channels that run the length of the roof end-to-end to help us achieve a rigid and silent assembly. The Can-Am Defender crew metal roof attaches via 6 points on the Defender's frame. 2 bolts in the front secure roof to factory slots in overhead roll-frame, while 4 stainless steel rubber coated loop-clamps secure to middle and rear roll frame.¬†

Due to the length of the Can-Am Defender Max Crew model UTV, ALL roofs are what would normally be our optional "extended" versions right off the bat. The roof has a great overhand on the front that helps protect from the elements and is windshield friendly!¬†

Can-Am Defender Max Metal Roof Specs

  • Steel Construction (Optional Aluminum Upgrade) with steel tubular/angle iron sub-frame
  • Textured Powder Coat standard (Optional Bed Liner Upgrade)
  • 14 Gauge Steel Shell¬†(Optional 11 Gauge Aluminum Upgrade)
  • Rain ‚ÄúGutters‚Äù Front & Rear
  • Direct fitment using factory holes and loop clamp fasteners. (Set the roof in place over the roll bar and use the pre-slotted holes on front of overhead pressed metal frame that came factory from Can-Am) No¬†modification, mounts perfectly to OEM Can-Am frame. 2 bolts in front, 2 loop clamps in center, 2 loop clamps in rear.¬†
  • Lifetime Warranty on construction

Can-Am Defender Max Metal Roof Compatibility:

  • 100% compatible with all: 2018+ Defender Max UTV's
    • Have full size doors? OR plan to put on full size doors? - Make sure you let us know you need "LOW PROFILE FLANGES" - in the Comment section at checkout or contact us directly to order.¬†

column2: Fortress Tip Out Windshield Kawasaki Mule Pro (FX & FXT)
column3:
Fortress tip out windshield for the Kawasaki Mule Pro FX & FXT UTV models is a solid option. Simply put, it allows for a mode that keeps windshield all the way open, or a vent mode (approximately 5 inches outward) allowing just air circulation.¬†

A powder coated metal frame that is formed perfectly to the front and overhead roll bar frame securely snugs the Fortress windshield with loop clamps. No noise, no rattle, no squeaks! Works with most roofs on the market including our Ranch Armor metal tops for the Mule Pro's. 2 gas shocks hold the windshield up when in upright position. Handle used to lock window down also acts as the prop lock to hold window in "vent" mode.¬†

**Fortress Tip-Out Windshield Works with our Kawasaki Mule Pro FXT Roofs without any interference or modification needed for either component. Get a bundle price when you purchase windshield with one of our RanchArmor Tops.**

column2: Polaris Ranger Quick Connect High Seat
column3:
Our newest Polaris Ranger High Seat is here!¬†The seat cushions are larger in width by 10 inches, while the updated laser cut tread plate foot platform has been extended 6 inches further out. Side standard baskets/beverage holders are also laser cut and pressed for a clean refined look.¬†¬†

Our Ranch Armor Polaris Ranger high seat features 4 steel pegs/legs that go down approximately 2 inches into factory holes on bed sides locking the seat to the bed sides. With 4 steel pipes going into factory Polaris lock-and-ride holes, this helps assure that the bed won't warp or bend outward from seat and weight over-time. The seat secures to the bed with 4 high strength turn-buckles that tie seat down to factory corner bed latches. Install is a breeze and can be done in less than 10 minutes.¬†

Getting in and out of the high seat is simple and convenient with folding ladders on both sides. The ladders use tread plate (commonly known as diamond plate) steps to help with grip when its wet and your boots are caked with mud! Foot platform is laser cut with a double return press on both sides out of 14 gauge tread plate. Nut certs are welded into the center front of the foot platform to allow for easy installation of rifle mounts. Drains are laser cut on floor plate to allow water, mud, etc, to fall into bed and not sit on surface.¬†

Polaris Ranger Quick Connect High Seat Specifications:

  • Constructed of steel¬†
  • Sail cloth UV, Marine, Mildew resistant fabric/canvas (10x stronger then vinyl)
  • Marine medium firm foam cushions
  • Laser-cut plate legs provide great look and exceptional support
  • Choice of a textured powder coat standard
  • Folding ladders that are removable
  • Lifetime warranty on construction

Ranch Armor High Seats are NOT to be ridden while vehicle is in motion. Please Note: Death or Serious Injury can occur.¬†

column2: John Deere XUV Quick Connect High Seat
column3:
¬†A high seat solution for the John Deere Gator XUV is here! A quick-connect seat that has been built from the ground up for the Gator XUV's. With a large foot platform that is extra wide and easy folding ladders, getting up in the seat is easy. Side plate-style legs that are laser cut cantilever back slightly giving passengers even more room while shooting their favorite trophy buck, not to mention it adds to the overall style of the seat.

Side storage baskets come standard to hold gear or your favorite beverage. Adjustable rifle rest mounts to the high seat foot platform and goes up or down six inches. If you would like additional storage you can add a rear upper high seat basket.¬†

John Deere Gator XUV high seats sit on an angle iron platform/foundation that hugs the bed-rails of the bed¬† (left, and right). Welded tie-down anchors on the bottom of the high seat foundation are what's used to latch and tighten seat frame to CanAm factory bed tie-downs.

We use a local Texas based vendor for our cushions that are constructed using marine grade firm-foam, and Sail cloth. The Sail cloth is 10x more durable than vinyl and is fully water, weather, and mildew resistant. Don't worry, it has a poly-urethane coating on it that makes it glossy and smooth.¬†

Ranch Armor High Seats are NOT to be ridden while vehicle is in motion. Please Note: Death or Serious Injury can occur.

column2: Kawasaki Mule Pro FX/DX Metal Top
column3:
Kawasaki Mule Pro FX Metal Roof specifically for the single cab FX UTV. Roof is the largest standard offering on the market for the Mule FX, and compliments the large over-size single cab frame nicely. Roof is plenty large and strong enough to handle up to 1000 pounds of overall weight. Use it to feel feeders, store cargo, and of course take advantage of the front overhang/lip to keep out of the sun or rain.¬†

Our Kawasaki Mule Pro FX metal tops are constructed using 14 gauge sheet metal (steel) for the shell, 1" channel and angle iron subframe, and a 3 inch tall laser cut and pressed/rolled over utility rack above. The standard roof rack has diagonal slots around the perimeter providing plenty of tie-down points and mounting locations for any tool/combo you could ever need. Don't forget the stylish Texas laser cut-outs we strategically placed throughout as well.¬†

A Kawasaki Mule Pro FXT Metal Roof that is rugged, looks good, and functional.¬†¬†

Kawasaki Mule Pro FX Metal Top Metal Roof Specs

  • Steel Construction with steel tubular/angle iron sub-frame
  • Textured Powder Coat standard
  • 14 Gauge Steel Shell¬†(Optional 11 Gauge Aluminum Upgrade)
  • Rain ‚ÄúGutters‚Äù Front & Rear
  • Direct fitment using factory holes. Easily bolts on using 4 bolts with no modification.¬†
  • Lifetime Warranty on construction

Kawasaki Mule Pro FX Metal Top COMPATIBILITY:

  • 100% compatible with all: 2015+ model Kawasaki Mule Pro FX UTV's.¬†
    • Have full size doors? OR plan to put on full size doors? - Make sure you let us know you need "LOW PROFILE FLANGES" - in the Comment section at checkout or contact us directly to order.¬†

column2: Polaris Ranger Pro-Fit Crew Metal Top
column3:
Polaris Ranger Full-Size Crew Standard Length Metal Top. One-piece design for solid construction and durability. The metal shell is fully welded construction sitting on a sub-frame skeleton that easily bolts to the pre-slotted holes on your full-size Polaris Ranger (570/900/1000) Pro-fit Crew frame. The sheet metal shell components are laser-cut for a 100% precise line all around.¬†

Will our roof fly off like maybe yours has already? Heck no! We have personally tested (very carefully of course) 100+ mph pulls being trailered on IH 10 in West Texas to make sure you'll never have to check the rear view mirror when transporting.¬†

(Pictures shown vary with different roof setups/options customers have decided to do. Build your roof using our standard package offerings or give us a call if you are looking for something custom.)

POLARIS RANGER 570/900/1000 CREW ONE-PIECE METAL TOP SPECS

  • Steel Construction (Optional Aluminum Upgrade) with steel tubular sub-frame
  • Textured Powder Coat standard (Optional Bed Liner Upgrade)
  • 14 Gauge Steel Shell (Optional 11 Gauge Aluminum Upgrade)
  • Rain ‚ÄúGutters‚Äù Front & Rear
  • Direct bolt-on for easy installation. (Set the roof in place over the roll bar and use the pre-slotted lock-n-ride holes that come factory from Polaris) No¬†modification, mounts perfectly to OEM Polaris frame
  • Lifetime Warranty on construction

POLARIS RANGER ONE-PIECE METAL ROOF COMPATIBILITY:

  • 100% compatible with all: 2014+ model Polaris Ranger 570, 900, 1000 Full-Size Crew Pro-Fit Frames (Geometry overhead has not changed on Pro-Fit Frames)¬†

column2: Kawasaki Mule Pro Front Roll Bar Basket
column3:
Kawasaki Mule Pro Series Roll bar basket by Ranch Armor. Fully compatible with most tip-out glass windshields. We try to stay away from U-bolts and this roll bar basket is no exception. It bolts-up easily using the pre-existing factory roll-cage bolts that connect chassis to upper roll-frame. It's as simple as undoing the factory bolts (2 on each side), and sliding roll-bar mounts in between two frame pieces.¬†

Kawasaki Mule Pro Fx/FXT Front Roll Bar Basket Specifications:

  • Laser Cut 14 GA Sheet Metal with Pressed Edges
  • Slotted and Vented Design
  • Laser-cut/Pressed mounts fit and contour perfect with roll-frame studs.
  • Textured powder-coat finish standard¬†
  • Hardware included to secure basket to roll-bar mounts. (2x bolts/2x lock-nuts/4x washers)
  • Install time: 20-30 minutes
  • Warranty: Lifetime on welds and construction

Kawasaki Mule Pro Basket Compatibility:

  • 100% compatible with all: 2015+ model Kawasaki Mule Pro Series UTV's.

column2: Kawasaki Mule Pro FX/FXT High Seat
column3:
A spacious and secure Kawasaki Mule Pro FX/FXT High Seat is here! The new Mule Pro models are well-built machines that follow in the footsteps of the Mule UTV line everyone has come to know. The Pro really has some get-up and drives phenomenally. The bed is smaller, which left us with a challenge in creating a high seat that would allow for two large adults to sit up safely. The solution was quickly found which involved extending the butt portion of the seat out, and hang over the tailgate. Of course, we had to make sure the seat was safe. We tested it through the most extreme conditions including: massive incline and declines as well as roll-over/tip testing. Torture testing on the unit was done with riders equating to over 500 pounds up on the seat. Disclaimer: As always, we DO NOT recommend and are always against riding high seats while vehicle(s) are in motion.¬†

We now include 2 additional braces that mount under-bed and utilize factory bed-frame tubing to reinforce front bolt-down points of high seat. Please see photo below or in product image gallery.

Kawasaki Mule Pro FX/FXT High Seat Specifications:

  • Primary construction - Steel: 1" Square Tube , Angle Iron, Laser cut 3/16" Thick Legs
  • Sail cloth UV, Marine, Mildew resistant fabric/canvas (10x stronger then vinyl)
  • Marine medium firm foam cushions
  • Laser-cut plate legs provide great look and exceptional support
  • Choice of a textured powder coat (standard) or Bed-Liner for additional cost
  • Lifetime warranty on construction

Ranch Armor High Seats are NOT to be ridden while vehicle is in motion. Please Note: Death or Serious Injury can occur.¬†

column2: Yamaha Viking 6 (IV) Metal Top
column3:
Yamaha Viking 6 crew metal roof is here! A true one-piece metal top for the Viking VI UTV. We were the first to offer a metal one-piece top for the Viking's. The reason we are first, and you're probably asking why didn't anyone else make it or why is there still only a couple companies making metal tops for them? It's NOT because the Viking isn't popular! Yamaha made the Viking UTV's frame wider than ANY other UTV on the market to accommodate the 6 individual passenger seat(s) arrangement. Available sheets of metal to accommodate are usually 5' x 10'. Well, the Viking needs a few inches wider at 62" being the widest over-head roll-frame width. It was a headache that we had no choice, but to address. It would not have been a problem if we did a two-piece metal roof, but we ran in the opposite direction of the two-piece designs back in early 2014.¬†

Roof mounts easily using included U-Bolt hardware, and is 100% silent. This top although larger over our other crew crew UTV roofs, is actually lighter. A lighter what we coined "frame-on-frame" design was used. Go ahead, stand up there, fill your feeders and put all the corn you want on the top, it won't mind one bit.¬†

Yamaha Viking IV (Crew) Metal Roof Specifications:

  • Steel Construction with steel tubular/Angle Iron sub-frame
  • Textured Powder Coat standard
  • 14 Gauge Steel Shell (Optional 11 Gauge Aluminum Upgrade)
  • Rain ‚ÄúGutters‚Äù Front & Rear
  • Easy Installation. (Set the roof in place over the roll bars and line-up loop-clamp slots)
  • Lifetime Warranty on construction

column2: Yamaha Viking High Seat
column3:
First true Quick Connect Yamaha Viking High Seat. Our high seats are built with pride and functionality. Viking's already have a hand above most other UTV brands with a stronger metal constructed bed, as opposed to plastic.

You have the option to have your Viking high seat coated with: standard textured powder coat, or for additional cost bed-liner.¬†

The seats and cushions are another game changer for the high seat world. We are very proud to use a material that is stronger and MUCH more durable than vinyl, it's called sail cloth. It is 100% water resistant, 3 layer UV canvas that is popularly used in the automotive world for convertible tops. It doesn't rip easily, it doesn't stretch, and it can take a beating from the sun and weather. Easily cleans with water and a microfiber towel.¬†

Yamaha Viking High Seat Specifications:

  • Constructed of steel (aluminum is optional)
  • Sail cloth UV, Marine, Mildew resistant fabric/canvas (10x stronger then vinyl)
  • Marine medium firm foam cushions
  • Laser-cut plate legs provide great look and exceptional support
  • Choice of a textured powder coat (standard) or Bed-liner for additional cost
  • Folding ladders that are removable
  • Lifetime warranty on construction

Ranch Armor High Seats are NOT to be ridden while vehicle is in motion. Please Note: Death or Serious Injury can occur.

column2: Quick Connect Mid-Size Polaris Ranger High Seat
column3:
Ranch Armor High Seats are NOT to be ridden while vehicle is in motion. Please Note: Death or Serious Injury can occur.¬†

Polaris Ranger Mid-Size Quick Connect Polaris Ranger high seat is here! Built specifically for the mid-size Polaris Ranger, our new mid-size high seat is packed with standard features. Four steel pipe/tubes on the bottom-side of platform extend 2 inches into factory holes/slots on bed-sides creating a very snug and precise fit.¬†

A HUGE laser-cut and CNC press broke foot/standing platform runs the full width of bed making moving around and standing simple. The cushions themselves went through multiple phases of testing, We ruled out vinyl (tears and becomes weak in direct sunlight) and went with Sail Cloth automotive-grade convertible top canvas. The cushions are UV and water resistant fitted over a firm marine-grade foam.¬†Easily adjust removable rifle rack 6 inches up or down. Yes, high seat will fit through a standard garage door (our most common question) without any issues! Dual folding ladders support up to 350 pounds, and can be completely taken off high rack within 30 seconds. The whole high seat has a straight standard powder coat.

Polaris Ranger Mid-Size 570/EV High Seat Options:

  • Constructed of steel (aluminum is optional)
  • Sail cloth UV, Marine, Mildew resistant fabric/canvas (10x stronger then vinyl)
  • Marine medium firm foam cushions
  • Laser-cut plate legs provide great look and exceptional support
  • Choice of a textured powder coat (standard) or Bed-liner for additional cost
  • Folding ladders that are removable
  • Lifetime warranty on construction

column2: Polaris Ranger Roll Bar Basket (Pro-Fit Frame)
column3:
Ranch Armor Roll Bar Basket for Polaris Ranger Full-Size Pro Fit 570/900/1000. It does NOT use U-Bolts. It bolts-up easily using the pre-existing factory roll-cage bolts that connect chassis to upper roll-frame. It's as simple as undoing the factory bolts (2 on each side), and sliding roll-bar mounts in between two frame pieces.¬†

Polaris Ranger 570/900/1000 Front Roll Bar Basket Specifications:

  • Laser Cut 14 GA Sheet Metal with Pressed Edges
  • Slotted and Vented Design
  • Laser-cut/Pressed mounts fit and contour perfect with roll-frame studs.
  • Textured powder-coat finish standard (Rhino bed liner shown in pics below available at additional cost)¬†
  • Hardware included to secure basket to roll-bar mounts. (2x bolts/2x lock-nuts/4x washers)
  • Install time: 20-30 minutes
  • Warranty: Lifetime on welds and construction

Polaris Ranger Pro Fit Basket Compatibility:

  • 100% compatible with all: 2014+ model Polaris Ranger Single Cab and Crew Cab: 570, 900, 1000 Full-Size Crew Pro-Fit Frames
